bgm.name: 04 はじめてファンタジー

parameters: \n<Velona>Better grab a seat, cause I'm gonna to be here awhile...
\n<Velona>Almost there... Jeez, why can't they just hire more people.
\n<Velona>My taxes are doing jack in this town.
\n<Velona>Good lord, I've been waiting here for ages...
\n<Angry Merc>What kind of operation are your running here!?
Please understand that today is one of the busiest days of the month.
\n<Angry Merc>Tch, the biggest guild in ALL of Tricora and this is
the kind of service you have to offer?
\n<Angry Merc>I don't pay these ludicrous quest acquisition fees
so you can stand around and chat.
\n<Guild Clerk>How may I help you today?
\n<Angry Merc>You better not miss a single galder.
\n<Angry Merc>I got a big night ahead of me and I need every penny!
\n<Velona>No no, you got the wrong person.
500,000 galders exact change in notes, no coins.
The girls I could buy with this.
You be my escort to Metro Vysio and I give you this wad of cash.
\n<Angry Merc>Buy you a nice dinner, some new clothes,
\n<Angry Merc>Not all the time I see such.. young blood at the guild.
\n<Angry Merc>Did you really just turn down 500 thousand Gs??
That's worth more than your entire life!
\n<Angry Merc>COCKY BRAT! I'll fucking kill you!
\n<Velona>Sheesh, I thought this guy was already trash
but he just went up like 50 tiers on the human garbage scale.
\n<Velona>I really don't want to hurt you.
\n<Angry Merc>Just what the hell kind of freak are you...?
\n<Angry Merc>Heh, no wonder you're so quick.
\n<Velona>Tch... You know full well I can't do that.
\n<Angry Merc>Hmph, guess I'll make my way then.
\n<Angry Merc>Hopefully, the next deity I meet ain't so...\|

parameters.name: 04 はじめてファンタジー

parameters: \n<Velona>Now I can finally get some money so I can
\n<Guild Clerk>Wow... I don't think I've ever seen anyone move that fast
I guess you clerks don't actually see much action outside these
\n<Guild Clerk>May I see your identification card please?
Name: Velona Hana Deglim          Address: 1 Kuroi Clearing, Vysio, Tricora
Class: Dawn Mage (DEITY)          Party Recruitment: Restricted
\n<Guild Clerk>Oh. That makes sense. You're a deity!
\n<Guild Clerk>I don't think I've ever met a deity before.
\n<Guild Clerk>Wow... It must be nice to be all-powerful and all that.
\n<Guild Clerk>And you're 214 and look like a kid!
\n<Guild Clerk>What's it like? To live so long???
To have crazy magic powers?? To have the power of gods???
\n<Velona>Considering I had to wait her all day because I need money.
\n<Guild Clerk>Oh. I suppose that does make some sense.
\n<Velona>You going to help me or what?
What was it you needed again?
\n<Guild Clerk>May I see your quest redemption form?
\n<Guild Clerk>Give me a moment while I calculate your payout.
\n<Guild Clerk>Your gross payout for this quest is: 20,000 galders.
\n<Guild Clerk>After deducting the guild fee, taxes, and applying the
deity reduction rate... your net payout comes out to:
Is there anything else I can help you with today?
\n<Velona>Nope, I'm all set. This all I came here for.
Please come back anytime for all of your guild needs!
Thank you for using the Vysio Guild!
\n<Velona>Sheesh, that girl must be new or something.
I just wanna run in and hit things with a big sword.
Who needs plans when you can just do a ton of damage!
Hmm... Perhaps if we attack like this we could maximize our damage
Goddamn, just sign the damn papers already!
Woo! I cannot wait to get paid!
Man, guarding pays well but having to fill out all this paperwork
